{"tid":1313605,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"便衣影大頭 應如何反應","createTime":"2019-07-13T22:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:25:10.000Z","uid":271396,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d86efc162e443f8117d7baf36c8fbf10d30b4d13","tid":1313605,"uid":271396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T22:22:20.000Z","msg":"戰術討論:<br />\n<br />\n成日有疑似便衣的人混入人群中影大頭，其實大叫黑警是無用，如果懷疑有人影大頭，女士應大聲話你做物影我個胸，老實講，影頭影胸都係差唔多角度。<br />\n<br />\n好了，旁人又可以做甚麼，罪案發生，仲唔用101拘捕令?<br />\n<br />\n《刑事罪行條例》下的「遊蕩」罪、普通法下的「破壞公眾體統」罪，以及《公安條例》下的「公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為」等控罪，皆曾被用來檢控偷拍者。<br />\n<br />\n當然大家要好好保護自己。"},{"pid":"93f873e18b69dc306398492d2e83022e1351abc4","tid":1313605,"uid":213631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f857f8ee2997af6997f090c3e01cb87bd67900","tid":1313605,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:38:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b4ae6ae751c097234ab19ee154319b319ccd5b0","tid":1313605,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cb0667e407702474c3a1f47b3789b4c454f0950","tid":1313605,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"afda080242d719cfe470c5cee1c56c0d2c0235eb","tid":1313605,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"呢個時候，POP子會點做？"},{"pid":"72d10fe7a2d5e73037073eeeaee3b367b27d395e","tid":1313605,"uid":220182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces